				<tr>
				
					<td class="gensmall" width="100%"><div style="float: left;">&nbsp;<b>Post subject:</b> <a href="#p196730">Re: Camerica Mapper 71 for games other than Fire Hawk</a></div><div style="float: right;"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=196730&amp;sid=bf68b31947ac6c82a1af1b0e7ee343be#p196730"><img src="./styles/subsilver2/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a><b>Posted:</b> Fri May 26, 2017 8:27 pm&nbsp;</div></td>
