				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Many mapper 7 games on the <a href="https://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/AxROM" class="postlink">ANROM or AOROM board</a> fall into &quot;Requires CPU's value to prevail over the ROM's value&quot; because they expect the PRG ROM to disable itself during writes. ANROM decodes PRG ROM with 74HC02, and AOROM uses a PRG ROM whose +CE is wired to CPU R/W.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

